						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged in part. It seems to register the gift of a village tax-free (probably with the income specified in paddy and gold) by prince Rājādityadēva for the expenses of worship in the main shrine of the temple of Śrī-Āṟṟuttaḷi at Muḍiyūr. </p>						

